sound%20of%20a%20poor%20network%2C%20her%20enthusiasm%20shines%20through%20as%20she%20exclaims%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20truly%20a%20blessing%20to%20be%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIshita%20is%20a%20student%20enrolled%20at%20Pathshala%2C%20a%20foundation%20led%20by%20Juin%20Datta%20in%20Vadodara.%20This%20organisation%20is%20committed%20to%20offering%20free%20education%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282848%2Fretired-teacher-gives-free-education-to-children-in-jammu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderprivileged%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20those%20from%20migrant%20workers%E2%80%99%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20a%20comprehensive%20range%20of%20essentials%20to%20our%20students%20here%20%E2%80%94%20from%20quality%20education%2C%20shelter%2C%20food%2C%20and%20clothing%20to%20promising%20opportunities%20for%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20stigma%20attached%20to%20joining%20school%20late%20because%20we%20operate%20differently%20from%20conventional%20schools.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FSupport-Srotoshwini-Trust%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonate%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FSupport-Srotoshwini-Trust%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20on%20the%20principles%20of%20project-based%20learning%2C%20the%20school%20eschews%20traditional%20grading%20systems%20in%20favour%20of%20levels.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20I%20might%20be%20at%20Level%204%20for%20Gujarati%20but%20Level%208%20for%20math.%20Age%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20determining%20factor%20here%3B%20what%20truly%20matters%20is%20your%20willingness%20to%20learn%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ishita%20explains%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIshita%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%2097%20children%20residing%20in%20the%20hostel%20provided%20by%20the%20Pathshala%20Foundation.%20The%20majority%20of%20them%20hail%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326013%2Fbengaluru-friends-run-gubacchi-non-profit-to-educate-migrant-worker-children-for-free%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%20migrant%20worker%20families%20%3C%2Fa%3Eunable%20to%20afford%20quality%20education.%20Thanks%20to%20Juin%E2%80%99s%20efforts%2C%20these%20children%20now%20have%20access%20to%20opportunities%20for%20a%20brighter%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20just%20a%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Pathshala%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(school)%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathshala%E2%80%99s%20journey%20began%20a%20decade%20ago%20as%20a%20mobile%20initiative%20providing%20free%20education.%20Juin%20elaborates%20on%20the%20inception%20of%20this%20initiative%20and%20recounts%20her%20decade-long%20endeavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20a%20bunch%20of%20chatty%20ladies%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Juin%2C%20recalling%202013%2C%20when%20the%20idea%20first%20came%20to%20her.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20school%20teacher%20back%20then%20and%20would%20get%20together%20with%20some%20friends%20from%20my%20community%20to%20have%20raving%20discussions%20about%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20of%20friends%20Juin%20refers%20to%20was%20a%20mix%20of%20teachers%20and%20other%20professionals%20who%20would%20meet%20periodically.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20one%20of%20such%20discussions%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20we%20were%20merely%20talking%20and%20not%20doing%20anything%20beyond%20that.%20As%20we%20were%20a%20bunch%20of%20teachers%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20do%20what%20we%20knew%20best%20%E2%80%94%20teach.%20So%20we%20started%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F129899%2Fgoa-construction-workers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego%20to%20a%20construction%20site%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20start%20teaching%20kids%20of%20the%20workers%20for%20free%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pathshala%20started%20as%20a%20mobile%20teaching%20initiative%20before%20Juin%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20residential%20school.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349408%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPathshala%20started%20as%20a%20mobile%20teaching%20initiative%20before%20Juin%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20residential%20school.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20to%20their%20efforts%20was%20good%2C%20so%20the%20group%20divided%20their%20efforts%20and%20started%20to%20teach%20in%20three%20different%20locations%20in%20Vadodara.%20%E2%80%9CWithin%20some%20months%2C%20from%20a%20dozen%20kids%2C%20we%20went%20to%20teaching%20hundreds.%20But%20the%20problem%20was%20that%20every%20six%20months%2C%20