would%20just%20take%20part%20in%20the%20protests%20here.%20We%20later%20came%20to%20know%20she%20is%20with%20the%20BJP.%20She%20should%20be%20punished%20for%20lying%20to%20us%20and%20trapping%20us.%20I'm%20sure%20more%20people%20were%20deceived%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%C2%A0The%20woman%20and%20her%20family%20said%20they%20are%20now%20receiving%20threats%20for%20coming%20out%20against%20Piyali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20on%20the%20backfoot%20after%20local%20party%20leaders%20were%20accused%20of%20rape%2C%20land%20grab%20and%20extortion%2C%20has%20latched%20on%20to%20the%20woman's%20allegations%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20cooking%20up%20stories%20to%20malign%20the%20ruling%20party%20for%20political%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20MP%20Sushmita%20Dev%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20threatening%20the%20%26quot%3Bcourageous%20women%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20for%20daring%20to%20speak%20out%20against%20them%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20longer%20will%20this%20party%20persist%20in%20spinning%20webs%20of%20deceit%2C%20shamelessly%20trampling%20on%20the%20dignity%20of%20our%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20for%20their%20own%20political%20greed%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20hit%20back%2C%20describing%20Trinamool's%20allegations%20as%20a%20damage%20control%20exercise%20that%20has%20come%20too%20late.%20Party%20spokesperson%20Priyanka%20Tibrewal%20said%20the%20Trinamool%20must%20understand%20that%20there%20is%20no%20use%20crying%20over%20spilt%20milk.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20Trinamool%20responding%20now%3F%20Why%20were%20they%20quiet%20for%20two-three%20months.%20They%20earlier%20said%20the%20women%20(of%20Sandeshkhali)%20were%20lying%2C%20now%20they%20are%20saying%20they%20were%20made%20to%20lie.%20Whatever%20damage%20had%20to%20happen%20has%20happened.%20There%20is%20no%20smoke%20without%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%2