video-fedex-boeing-767-lands-without-front-landing-gear-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Smoke%20and%20sparks%20are%20seen%20coming%20from%20the%20Boeing%20jet%20as%20the%20nose%20scrapes%20along%20the%20tarmac%20at%20Istanbul%20Airport.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22psyme%40businessinsider.com%20(Pete%20Syme)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-fedex-boeing-767-lands-without-front-landing-gear-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindu%20Population%20Fell%207.8%25%20Between%201950-2015%2C%20Muslims%20Up%2043.15%25%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20share%20of%20the%20Hindu%20population%20decreased%20by%207.82%20per%20cent%20between%201950%20and%202015%20in%20India%2C%20while%20that%20of%20Muslims%20increased%20by%2043.15%20per%20cent%2C%20suggesting%20that%20there%20is%20a%20conducive%20environment%20in%20the%20country%20to%20foster%20diversity%2C%20said%20a%20recent%20working%20paper%20by%20the%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(EAC-PM).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20titled%20'Share%20of%20Religious%20Minorities%3A%20A%20Cross-Country%20Analysis%20(1950-2015)'%20further%20said%20the%20share%20of%20Jains%20in%20the%20population%20of%20India%20decreased%20from%200.45%20per%20cent%20in%201950%20to%200.36%20per%20cent%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20Hindu%20population%20decreased%20by%207.82%20per%20cent%20between%201950%20and%202015%20(from%2084.68%20per%20cent%20to%2078.06%20per%20cent).%20The%20share%20of%20Muslim%20population%20in%201950%20was%209.84%20per%20cent%20and%20increased%20to%2014.09%20per%20cent%20in%202015%20--%20a%2043.15%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20their%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20paper%20prepared%20by%20a%20team%20led%20by%20Shamika%20Ravi%2C%20member%2C%20EAC-PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20paper%2C%20the%20share%20of%20Christian%20population%20rose%20from%202.24%20per%20cent%20to%202.36%20per%20cent%20--%20an%20increase%20of%205.38%20per%20cent%20between%201950%20and%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20share%20of%20Sikh%20population%20increased%20from%201.24%20per%20cent%20in%201950%20to%201.85%20per%20cent%20in%202015%20-%20a%206.58%20per%20cent%20rise%20in%20their%20share%2C%20the%20share%20of%20the%20Parsi%20population%20in%20India%20witnessed%20a%20stark%2085%20per%20cent%20decline%2C%20reducing%20from%200.03%20per%20cent%20share%20in%201950%20to%200.004%20per%20cent%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20indicates%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20a%20conducive%20environment%20to%20foster%20diversity%20in%20the%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20paper%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20promote%20better%20life%20outcomes%20for%20the%20disadvantaged%20sections%20of%20society%20without%20providing%20a%20nurturing%20environment%20and%20societal%20support%20through%20a%20bottom-up%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20noted%20that%20a%20decrease%20in%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20population%20and%20a%20consequent%20increase%20in%20the%20share%20of%20minorities%20suggests%20that%20the%20net%20result%20of%20all%20policy%20actions%2C%20political%20decisions%20and%20societal%20processes%20is%20to%20provide%20a%20conducive%20environment%20for%20increasing%20diversity%20in%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20pointed%20out%20that%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20global%20trends%20of%20declining%20majority%2C%20India%20too%20has%20witnessed%20a%20reduction%20in%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20denomination%20by%207.82%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20particularly%20remarkable%20given%20the%20wider%20context%20within%20the%20South%20Asian%20neighborhood%20where%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20denomination%20has%20increased%20and%20minority%20populations%20have%20shrunk%20alarmingly%20across%20countries%20like%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Bhutan%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20paper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20said%20it%20is%20not%20surprising%2C%20therefore%2C%20minority%20populations%20from%20across%20the%20neighborhood%20come%20to%20India%20during%20times%20of%20duress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20pointed%20out%20that%20all%20the%20Muslim%20majority%20countries%20witnessed%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20denomination%20except%20Maldives%2C%20where%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20group%20(Shafi'i%20Sunnis)%20declined%20by%201.47%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bangladesh%2C%20there%20was%20an%2018%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20group%20which%20is%20the%20largest%20such%20increase%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent.%20Pakistan%20witnessed%20an%20increase%20of%203.75%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20denomination%20(Hanafi%20Muslim)%20and%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20the%20share%20of%20total%20Muslim%20population%20despite%20the%20creation%20of%20Bangladesh%20in%201971.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20among%20non-Muslim%20majority%20countries%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20India%20and%20Nepal%20saw%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20denomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20noted%20that%20the%20year%201950%20is%20important%20as%20a%20baseline%20year%20for%20two%20major%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20around%20the%20time%20that%20the%20international%20human%20rights%20framework%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20newly%20created%20United%20Nations%20began%20to%20take%20shape%20with%20minority%20rights%20and%20state%20responsibility%20for%20protection%20of%20minorities%20being%20mainstreamed%20in%20international%20law%2C%20the%20paper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20is%20a%20detailed%20cross-country%20descriptive%20analysis%20of%20the%20status%20of%20minorities%20around%20the%20world%20measured%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20changing%20share%20in%20a%20country's%20population%20over%2065%20years%20between%201950%20and%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20167%20countries%20analysed%2C%20the%20average%20value%20for%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20denomination%20in%20the%20baseline%20year%20of%201950%20is%2075%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20the%20mean%20of%20the%20distribution%20capturing%20the%20change%20in%20majority%20religious%20denomination%20between%201950%20and%202015%20is%2021.9.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715249760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fjrmv5a_population-generic-india-ians_625x300_09_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-population-fell-7-8-between-1950-2015-muslims-up-43-15-centres-report-5624094%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hindu%20population%20fell%20by%207.82%20per%20cent%20between%201950%20and%202015%20in%20India%2C%20while%20that%20of%20Muslims%20increased%20by%2043.15%20per%20cent%2C%20suggesting%20that%20there%20is%20a%20conducive%20environment%20in%20the%20country%20to%20foster%20diversity%2C%20said%20a%20recent%20working%20paper%20by%20the%20Centre.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-population-fell-7-8-between-1950-2015-muslims-up-43-15-centres-report-5624094%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-population-fell-7-8-between-1950-2015-muslims-up-43-15-centres-report-5624094%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-population-fell-7-8-between