rs-20-698-cr-nii-up-3-13-124050900631_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20is%20my%20third%20Mother's%20Day%20since%20divorce.%20I%20get%20no%20surprises%20or%20days%20off%2C%20but%20time%20with%20my%20son%20is%20everything%20I%20want.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Happy%20small%20boy%20kissing%20his%20mother%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663a6e8710dfcda40967b0aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETatiana%20Lavrova%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI've%20been%20divorced%20for%20three%20years%20and%20Mother's%20Day%20looks%20different%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20don't%20get%20a%20break%20from%20parenting%20nor%20do%20I%20get%20surprises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStill%2C%20I%20cherish%20time%20with%20my%20son%20over%20any%20present.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20was%20married%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fgifts%2Fbest-mothers-day-gifts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMother's%20Day%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20a%20much-needed%20break%20from%20parenting%20responsibilities.%20I%20slept%20in%20and%20decided%20how%20to%20spend%20the%20day%2C%20including%20coffee%20in%20bed%2C%20a%20late%20brunch%2C%20and%20a%20small%20token%20from%20my%20son.%20I%20still%20cherish%20the%20mug%20he%20gave%20me%20on%20my%20last%20pre-divorce%20Mother's%20Day.%20It%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BMom%20is%20the%20heart%20of%20our%20family.%26quot%3B%20In%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%2C%20that%20hasn't%20changed.%20I'm%20still%20the%20heart%20of%20our%20family%20unit%20%E2%80%94%20that%20unit%20has%20just%20become%20smaller.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20I'd%20be%20lying%20if%20I%20said%20that%20celebrating%20Mother's%20Day%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-dating-men-without-kids-no-fathers-less-complicated-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20single%20mom%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20hasn't%20been%20a%20difficult%2C%20and%20sometimes%20lonely%2C%20transition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BExpect%20there%20to%20be%20some%20hard%20moments%20during%20the%20day%2C%20and%20rather%20than%20try%20to%20push%20them%20down%20when%20they%20come%20up%2C%20just%20bring%20your%20presence%20to%20these%20feelings%20and%20experiences%20as%20they%20pop%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.carlnassar.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECarl%20Nassar%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20therapist%20specializing%20in%20emotional%20and%20mental%20well-being%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20all%2C%20you%20deserve%20compassion%20on%20this%20day%20most%20of%20all%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20wonderful%20gift%20to%20yourself%20on%20Mother's%20Day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20year%20will%20be%20my%20third%20time%20celebrating%20the%20holiday%20as%20a%20single%20mom.%20Though%20it's%20a%20day%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-new-social-media-app-nospace-nostalgic-less-curated-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enostalgia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20can%20easily%20take%20over%2C%20I've%20learned%20not%20to%20let%20feelings%20of%20loss%20run%20the%20show.%20Instead%2C%20I%20cherish%20Mother's%20Day%20as%20a%20single%20mom.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222eefdc6c-347f-41ba-83af-ccfd2a5c5c45%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EI'll%20take%20time%20with%20my%20son%20over%20gifts%20any%20day%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20I%20used%20to%20indulge%20my%20introversion%20during%20Mother's%20Day%2C%20sometimes%20heading%20out%20for%20hours%20to%20hike%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkarl-meltzer-48-year-old-sets-appalachian-trail-record-2016-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAppalachian%20trail%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20all%20I%20care%20about%20now%20is%20the%20extra%20moments%20with%20my%20child.%20I%20share%20custody%20of%20my%20son%20with%20his%20father%2C%20which%20means%20I%20don't%20get%20to%20see%20him%20every%20day.%20But%20our%20divorce%20agreement%20states%20that%20each%20parent%20gets%20to%20spend%20Mother's%20or%20Father's%20Day%20with%20our%20child%2C%20respectively.%20For%20me%2C%20Mother's%20Day%20is%20a%20bonus%20weekend%20of%20precious%20moments%20with%20my%20son.%20And%20I%20want%20to%20maximize%20that%20time%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20key%20to%20truly%20enjoying%20ourselves%20in%20the%20moment%20is%20to%20slow%20down%2C%20Nassar%20told%20BI.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20plan%20a%20few%20activities%2C%20but%20don't%20overdo%20it%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20way%2C%20you'll%20have%20time%20to%20lean%20into%20your%20time%20at%20the%20park%20and%20joke%20around%20and%20play%2C%20and%20if%20you%20spontaneously%20decide%20to%20stop%20for%20ice%20cream%20on%20the%20way%20home%2C%20there's%20time%20for%20that%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Nassar%20said.%20That's%20why%20I%20prefer%20leaving%20Mother's%20Day%20fairly%20open.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c3fdc84b-72a4-458d-917f-46a20e3f490d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20So%20what%20if%20I%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20my%20own%20brunch%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20days%2C%20the%20weekends%20are%20less%20about%20relaxing%20than%20fitting%20it%20all%20in.%20Errands%2C%20practice%2C%20obligations%2C%20and%20all%20the%20other%20things%20on%20our%20to-do%20lists%20leave%20little%20time%20for%20connection.%20On%20Mother's%20Day%2C%20we%20lounge%20around%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20get%20ready%20slowly%2C%20and%20head%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-breakfast-dishes-to-order-according-to-chef-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elate%20brunch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20things%20I've%20always%20loved%20the%20most%20about%20the%20holiday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENassar%20said%20spending%20the%20day%20with%20others%20can%20help%20make%20Mother's%20Day%20as%20a%20single%20mom%20easier.%20%26quot%3BChoose%20someone%20you%20feel%20comfortable%20being%20genuine%20and%20vulnerable%20with%2C%20and%20share%20your%20feelings%20%E2%80%94%20the%20good%20and%20the%20bad%20%E2%80%94%20so%20you're%20not%20alone%20in%20all%20you're%20going%20through%20on%20this%20Mother's%20Day.%26quot%3B%20When%20you're%20feeling%20down%2C%20there's%20nothing%20like%20a%20true%20connection%20with%20others%20to%20turn%20things%20around.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20continued%20my%20brunch%20tradition%20but%20with%20a%20twist.%20Instead%20of%20going%20it%20alone%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20widen%20my%20circle.%20Last%20year%2C%20I%20invited%20two%20of%20my%20neighbors%2C%20both%20widowed%2C%20to%20join%20me%20and%20my%20son%20for%20brunch.%20We%20enjoyed%20each%20other's%20company%2C%20and%20the%20meal%20was%20genuinely%20joyous.%20The%20best%20part%3F%20The%20last%20thing%20on%20any%20of%20our%20minds%20was%20being%20alone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmothers-day-after-divorce-means-no-surprises-days-off-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715248261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663a6e9f10dfcda40967b0b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmothers-day-after-divorce-means-no-surprises-days-off-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I've%20been%20divorc