h%2C%20and%20b)%20how%20the%20child%20was%20permitted%20to%20accompany%20his%20father%20into%20the%20booth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20has%20turned%20the%20Election%20Commission%20into%20a%20child's%20plaything.%20In%20Bhopal%2C%20the%20BJP's%20district%20panchayat%20member%20Vinay%20Mehar%20got%20his%20minor%20son%20to%20cast%20his%20vote.%20Vinay%20Mehar%20also%20made%20a%20video%20of%20the%20time%20when%20he%20cast%20his%20vote.%20Vinay%20Mehar%20posted%20the%20video%20on%20Facebook.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20there%20be%20any%20action%3F%26quot%3B%20Piyush%20Babele%2C%20whose%20X%20handle%20describes%20him%20as%20a%20media%20advisor%20in%20the%20office%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20said%20as%20he%20shared%20the%20video%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20has%20not%20yet%20responded%20to%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20has%20been%20acknowledged%20by%20district%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Collector%20Kaushalendra%20Vikram%20Singh%20has%20ordered%20an%20investigation%20and%20said%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20Presiding%20Officer%20at%20the%20polling%20booth%20and%20any%20persons%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Berasia%20Assembly%20segment%2C%20where%20the%20incident%20took%20place%2C%20is%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Caste%20candidates%2C%20and%20is%20one%20of%20eight%20that%20makes%20up%20the%20Bhopal%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Berasia%20segment%20is%20held%20by%20the%20BJP's%20Vishnu%20Khatre%2C%20while%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20is%20held%20by%20the%20party's%20Pragya%20Thakur%2C%20who%20thumped%20the%20Congress'%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20in%20the%20last%20election.%20She%20will%20not%2C%20though%2C%20defend%20her%20seat%20as%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20Alok%20Sharma%20against%20the%20Congress'%20Arun%20Shrivastava.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715248260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com