rt-advice-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epivot%20into%20a%20new%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20took%20me%20two%20years%20of%20connecting%2C%20trying%2C%20and%20failing.%20I%20found%20the%20framework%20of%20what%20Doux%20is%20now%20by%20failing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20in%20fashion%2C%20I%20got%20myself%20into%20medical%20sales.%20I%20then%20switched%20to%20tech%20because%20that's%20where%20my%20passions%20lie.%20It%20took%20me%20two%20years%20to%20go%20from%20fashion%20to%20medical%20sales.%20But%20from%20the%20day%20I%20decided%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20tech%20consultant%2C%20it%20only%20took%20me%20three%20weeks%20to%20get%20my%20offer%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20was%20I%20knew%20how%20to%20write%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20I%20knew%20how%20to%20become%20the%20candidate%20that%20they%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20formula%20is%20to%20map%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20to%20the%20career%20you're%20going%20to%2C%20not%20the%20career%20you've%20been%20in.%20To%20get%20to%20my%20current%20job%2C%20I%20created%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20that%20was%20unstoppable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20I%20tell%20my%20clients%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20hiring%20manager.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20the%20hiring%20manager%20got%20to%20me%20within%20minutes%20of%20me%20submitting%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20The%20interview%20process%20was%20extensive%2C%20but%2C%20like%20I%20always%20tell%20my%20clients%2C%20it's%20about%20follow-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20followed%20up%20three%20times%20because%20they%20had%20great%20candidates.%20But%20I%20needed%20to%20stay%20in%20front%2C%20and%20I%20needed%20to%20be%20the%20person%20they%20chose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22291cb78c-d2e6-4e15-b54c-8a87bf925169%5C%22%3EI%20had%20the%20drive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20funny%20when%20I%20look%20back%20and%20talk%20to%20the%20executives%20who%20hired%20me.%20They're%20like%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20had%20no%20business%20being%20in%20tech.%20You%20had%20nothing%20on