rovement%20in%20BPS%20(bits%20per%20second)%20that%20has%20now%20superseded%20Noland's%20initial%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fneuralink.com%2Fblog%2Fprime-study-progress-update-user-experience%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20the%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20despite%20the%20retraction%20of%20threads%2C%20Mr%20Arbaugh%20is%20using%20the%20company's%20system%20for%20around%20eight%20hours%20a%20day%20during%20the%20week%2C%20and%20often%20as%20many%20as%2010%20hours%20a%20day%20on%20the%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20with%20the%20implant%20was%20reported%20by%20Mr%20Arbaugh%20himself%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Fneuralinks-first-brain-chip-implant-in-a-human-appeared-flawless-there-was-a-problem-637f1adc%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%20(WSJ)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Neuralink%20considered%20removing%20the%20implant%2C%20as%20per%20the%20outlet%2C%20but%20the%20problem%20hasn't%20posed%20a%20direct%20risk%20to%20the%20man's%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeuralink%20shared%20its%20blog%20post%20after%20the%20Journal%20asked%20the%20company%20about%20the%20issue%2C%20according%20to%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20device%20was%20implanted%20in%20January%202024%20and%20Neuralink%20streamed%20a%20live%20video%20with%20Mr%20Arbaugh%20in%20March.%20The%20company%20had%20said%20that%20the%20surgery%20went%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20well%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715246220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fk88hjr0g_noland-arbaugh_625x300_24_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fneuralink-says-its-first-brain-chip-implant-has-encountered-a-problem-5624317%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20problem%20with%20Neuralink's%20brain%20implant%20was%20reported%20by%20Noland%20Arbaugh%2C%20who%20received%20it%20in%20January%20this%20year.%22%2C%22au