Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20November%2C%20I%20embarked%20on%20a%20trip%20where%20I%20spent%20several%20weeks%20leading%20my%20company%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-live-work-remote-on-cruise-ship-full-time-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efrom%20a%20cruise%20ship%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20my%20wife%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20We%20ultimately%20circumnavigated%20the%20globe%20on%20two%20different%20cruises%20and%20with%20air%20travel.%20Leaving%20California%2C%20we%20went%20through%20Europe%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Thailand%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20cool%20experience.%20But%20I%20found%20that%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-on-cruise-ship-full-time-residents%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20on%20the%20ship%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20do%20need%20some%20discipline%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20on%20a%2021-day%20cruise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c5a2683b-4e04-44e9-99bc-13d4657c9b9c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20have%20to%20create%20a%20time%20for%20work%20and%20a%20time%20for%20play%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20realize%20it%2C%20but%20when%20we%20upgraded%20our%20internet%2C%20it%20upgraded%20our%20drinks%20package.%20So%2C%20it%20turned%20out%20we%20could%20get%20bottles%20of%20Mo%C3%ABt%20%26amp%3B%20Chandon%20Champagne%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20couple%20of%20lunches%20and%20dinners%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fgifts%2Fbest-champagne%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewe%20enjoyed%20Champagne%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20we%20also%20developed%20a%20rhythm%20where%20we%20had%20work%20time%20and%20playtime.%20It%20wasn't%20rigid%20%E2%80%94%20but%20there%20were%20times%20when%20my%20wife%2C%20who%20does%20finance%20at%20UEGroup%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20we%20had%20to%20get%20things%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20can%20set%20you%20apart%20from%20people%20who%20are%20on%20vacation.%20That%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20can't%20work%20in%20your%20bathing%20suit%20or%20have%20a%20beer%20before%20you%20start%20your%20work%2C%20but%20it%20puts%20you%20on%20a%20slightly%20different%20footing%20than%20some%20of%20the%20other%20people%20on%20the%20cruise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf52fd81-8ba6-4a47-aa2b-2890314ad643%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpect%20very%20slow%20internet%20service%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20I%20didn't%20realize%20prior%20to%20the%20trip%20was%20that%20the%20cruise%20ship%20had%20only%20one%20satellite%20connection%20shared%20by%20thousands%20of%20people.%20The%20internet%20was%20oppressively%20slow%20at%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20our%20next%20long%20trip%2C%20I'm%20looking%20into%20getting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-t-mobile-starlink-satellites-mobile-cell-phones-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20satellite%20phone%20%3C%2Fa%3Eso%20I%20can%20put%20an%20antenna%20on%20my%20patio%20facing%20the%20right%20direction%20for%20the%20satellite.%20I've%20still%20got%20to%20figure%20it%20out%2C%20but%20there%20were%20times%20when%20it%20was%20really%20important%20for%20us%20to%20communicate%2C%20and%20we%20couldn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20now%20very%20mistrustful%20of%20statements%20the%20cruise%20lines%20make%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20their%20internet.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20upgraded%20our%20Internet%2C%20but%20it%20turned%20out%20the%20cruise%20line's%20definition%20of%20upgrading%20was%20that%20we%20could%20have%20more%20than%20one%20device%2C%20not%20that%20there%20was%20any%20better%20speed%20or%20reliability.%20You've%20got%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-you-should-not-buy-on-cruise-ship-to-save-money-2022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eread%20the%20fine%20print%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20how%20they%20define%20an%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20also%20recommend%20asking%20what%20kind%20of%20download%20and%20upload%20speeds%20to%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fe1b2913-7cc2-4982-80f6-efab79129beb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreate%20a%20backup%20plan%20for%20meetings%20and%20other%20communication%20challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-remote-from-cruise-ship-stay-productive-sea-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternet%20access%20can%20be%20unpredictable%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20with%20research%20and%20planning%20ahead%2C%20so%20we%20had%20backup%20people%20for%20important%20meetings%20back%20at%20the%20office.%20If%20we%20weren't%20able%20to%20show%20up%2C%20there%20was%20someone%20prepared%20with%20the%20slide%20deck.%20I%20can't%20say%20it%20didn't%20create%20awkward%20moments%20at%20times%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20downsides%20%E2%80%94%20but%20you%20can%20plan%20for%20it%20the%20best%20you%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20wife%20was%20dealing%20with%20a%20bank%20and%20needed%20to%20get%20a%20two-factor%20authentication%20code%20without%20working%20SMS%2C%20there%20wasn't%20much%20she%20could%20do.%20So%2C%20that%20was%20a%20challenge%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20points%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20go%20ashore%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternational-sim-card-unlock-iphone-android-business-travel-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20SIM%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20leverage%20local%20cell%20service%2C%20but%20this%20requires%20research.%20Depending%20on%20the%20country%20there%20might%20only%20be%20one%20cellphone%20service%20that%20works%20there%2C%20or%20you%20might%20be%20able%20to%20get%20SIM%20card%20brands%20that%20work%20for%20a%20larger%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d185bba3-2cdc-4ad8-9c4d-2d715c6ef114%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20offline%20can%20end%20up%20being%20a%20good%20thing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20be%20offline%2C%20but%20because%20the%20connectivity%20was%20so%20bad%20sometimes%2C%20it%20just%20forced%20it%20to%20happen.%20We%20were%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20nowhere%2C%20and%20it%20wasn't%20going%20to%20change.%20In%20a%20way%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-staying-off-phone-limiting-screen-time-cut-down-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeing%20offline%20was%20good%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20I%20could%20just%20tune%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20plan%20to%20cruise%20more%20in%20the%20future%20and%20even%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-moving-to-portugal-golden-visa-d7-overcrowding-housing-costs-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebought%20a%20home%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fa%3E%20near%20a%20cruise%20port%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20commute%20to%20using%20cruises%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20did%20the%20math%2C%20taking%20a%20cruise%20from%20California%20to%20Portugal%20was%20less%20than%20two%20business-class%20air%20travel%20tickets.%20Plus%2C%20you%20get%20meals%2C%20entertainment%2C%20and%20no%20jet%20lag%20%E2%80%94%20it%20seems%20like%20the%20way%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20live%20or%20work%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship%20and%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20story%2C%20please%20email%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amlogan%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emlogan%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-expect-working-remotely-on-cruise-ship-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715245562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66325eaf0dfb1341e9013331%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsi