-consultant-says-gen-z-are-misusing-ai-to-generate-cover-letters.html%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20career%20consultant%20explained%20that%20%26quot%3Bemployers%20have%20been%20suspecting%20that%20job%20seekers%20have%20been%20using%20ChatGPT%20after%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20hundreds%20of%20the%20exact%20same%20cover%20letters%20word%20for%20word%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20answers%20to%20job%20application%20questions%20that%20are%20the%20same.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3ECNBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Canva%20survey%20revealed%2045%25%20of%20job%20seekers%20have%20used%20AI%20to%20build%2C%20update%20or%20improve%20their%20resume.%20And%20it%20appears%20that%20gen%20Z%20is%20leaning%20the%20most%20on%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Grammarly%20survey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwomen-only-exhibit-in-australian-museum-to-become-toilet-to-keep-men-out-5623094%5C%22%3EWomen-Only%20Exhibit%20In%20Australian%20Museum%20To%20Become%20Toilet%20To%20Keep%20Men%20Out%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Davis%20said%20that%20while%20we%20should%20definitely%20%26quot%3Bembrace%20technology%20and%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20copying%20answers%20from%20ChatGPT%20can%20hurt%20your%20chances%20of%20getting%20a%20job.%20She%20also%20shared%20a%20recent%20incident%20with%20a%20recruiter%20hiring%20for%20a%20brand%20marketing%20position.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20candidates%20were%20asked%20a%20question%20in%20the%20job%20application%20about%20their%20favourite%20fitness-related%20product%20launches%20in%20the%20past%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20said%20they%20got%20about%20100%20identical%20responses%20of%20'my%20favourite%20campaign%20launch%20was%20Peloton'%20and%20the%20employer%20was%20like%20'ultimately%20that%20was%20ChatGPT%2C%20but%20then%20also%20equally%20Peloton%20was%20released%20like%20four%20or%20five%20years%20ago'%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Davis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20career%20consultant%20added%20that%20young%20people%20%26quot%3Bneed%20to%20educate%20themselves%26quot%3B%20on%20how%20to%20use%20ChatGPT%20properly%20and%20not%20just%20copy%20answers.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715243280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fb8ea8jsg_chatgpt_625x300_26_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fexact-same-cover-letters-career-consultant-explains-how-genz-are-misusing-ai-5623948%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shoshana%20Davis%2C%20a%20Gen%20Z%20career%20expert%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20career%20consultancy%20Fairy%20Job%20Mother%2C%20told%20CNBC%20Make%20It%20that%20young%20professionals%20have%20been%20making%20mistakes%20with%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20to%20generate%20job%20application%20answers%20and%20cover%20letters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fexact-same-cover-letters-career-consultant-explains-how-genz-are-misusing-ai-5623948%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fexact-same-cover-letters-career-consultant-explains-how-genz-are-misusing-ai-5623948%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fexact-same-cover-letters-career-consultant-explains-how-genz-are-misusing-ai-5623948%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'If%20this%20doesn't%20wake%20KL%20up...'%3A%20Ex-NZ%20pacer%20on%20Rahul's%20approach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715243039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109975265%2Cimgsize-77844.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fif-this-doesnt-wake-kl-rahul-up-former-new-zealand-pacer-calls-out-lsg-skippers-approach-against-srh%2Far