-years-kota-student-19-goes-missing-5623329%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LSG%20Owner's%20On-Camera%20Outburst%20At%20KL%20Rahul%3A%20Pure%20Emotion%20Or%20Toxic%20Culture%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20owner's%20call...they%20spend%20the%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravi%20Shastri%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41719-ravishankar-jayadritha-shastri-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavi%20Shastri%3C%2Fa%3E's%20comments%20on%20Mumbai%20Indians%20captaincy%20change%20seems%20more%20profound%20today%2C%20after%20what%20played%20out%20on%20Indian%20national%20television%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20owner%20Sanjiv%20%C2%A0Goenka's%20verbally%20bashing%20his%20IPL%20team's%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20following%20a%2010-wicket%20thrashing%20by%20SunRisers%20Hyderabad%2C%20is%20a%20scene%20that%20is%20being%20replayed%20ever%20since.%C2%A0%20It%20was%20the%20biggest%20loss%20in%20IPL%20history%20as%20SRH%20chased%20down%20a%20166-run%20target%20in%20just%2058%20balls.%20With%2062%20balls%20remaining%20in%20the%20innings%20it%20is%20the%20most%20dominating%20win%20in%20IPL%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20balls%20to%20spare%20(100%2B%20targets).%20Naturally%2C%20Goenka%2C%20a%20very%20successful%20industrialist%20and%20also%20the%20co-owner%20of%20ISL%20runner-up%20Mohun%20Bagan%20Super%20Giant%2C%20was%20not%20a%20happy%20man.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Goenka%20had%20bid%20over%20Rs%207000%20crore%20to%20buy%20LSG%20franchise%20in%20IPL.%20According%20to%20several%20reports%2C%20Goenka%20will%20pay%20BCCI%20a%20franchise%20of%20Rs%207090%20crore%20over%2010%20years.%20With%20him%20ready%20to%20shell%20out%20such%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20money%2C%20the%20attachment%20that%20Goenka%20has%20with%20the%20team%20is%20very%20apparent.%20His%20franchise%20has%20done%20well%20too%20in%20the%20past%2C%20reaching%20the%20playoffs%20in%20its%20first%20two%20years%20under%20KL%20Rahul's%20captaincy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20however%2C%20things%20seemed%20to%20be%20different.%20Though%20playoffs%20hopes%20are%20not%20lost%2C%20LSG%20are%20in%20a%20tricky%20spot.%20The%20team%20is%20sixth%20among%2010%20teams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%2010-wicket%20thrashing%20to%20SRH%20has%20added%20to%20the%20woes.%20And%20it%20seemed%2C%20it%20was%20too%20much%20for%20Goenka%20to%20handle.%20Throughout%20the%20match%2C%20Goenka%20could%20be%20seen%20following%20the%20match%20quite%20closely.%20Following%20the%20loss%2C%20however%2C%20emotion%20seemed%20to%20take%20control.%20Even%20the%20broadcaster%20could%20not%20help%20but%20term%20the%20interaction%20between%20Goenka%20and%20Rahul%20as%20%26quot%3Banimated%20reaction%20from%20LSG%20camp%26quot%3B.%20Even%20LSG%20coach%20and%20Australia%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Justin%20Langer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F267-justin-langer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJustin%20Langer%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20not%20spared%20either%2C%20as%20Goenka%20seemed%20to%20given%20him%20an%20earful%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20through%20this%20while%2C%20Rahul%20and%20Langer%2C%20stayed%20calm%20and%20took%20it%20all%20in.%20Rarely%20has%20such%20a%20scene%20been%20telecast%20on%20national%20television.%20But%2C%20can%20the%20readers%20vouch%20and%20say%20such%20incidents%20don't%20happen%20every%20day%20in%20boardrooms%20and%20corporate%20houses%3F%20Does%20this%20win%20at%20all%20cost%20mentality%20not%20play%20out%20daily%20at%20all%20work%20place%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20recently%2C%20two%20videos%20went%20viral%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20where%20officers%20of%20Bandhan%20Bank%20and%20Canara%20Bank%20can%20be%20seen%20reprimanding%20their%20junior%20employees%20using%20foul%20language%20over%20failing%20to%20meet%20targets.%20%C2%A0A%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20similar%20such%20incident%20happened%20in%20another%20bank%20and%20the%20foul-mouthing%20official%20was%20suspended.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoenka's%20case%20got%20more%20highlighted%20as%20he%20is%20a%20celebrated%20name.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20he%20may%20have%20momentarily%20forgotten%20that%20with%20the%20plethora%20of%20cameras%20on%20ground%2C%20nothing%20stays%20hidden.%20He%20has%20every%20right%20to%20feel%20bad%20about%20his%20team's%20loss%2C%20but%20to%20vent%20out%20his%20frustration%20at%20his%20captain%20on%20cricket%20matters%2C%20for%20which%20he%20has%20hired%20specialist%20support%20staff%2C%20was%20that%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20for%20every%20serious%20discussion%2C%20there%20is%20a%20thing%20called%20'closed%20door%20meeting'%2C%20something%20which%20the%20official%20broadcaster's%20also%20mentioned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaybe%20he%20could%20have%20taken%20a%20cue%20from%20how%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Rides%20co-owner%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20reacted%20after%20his%20side's%20loss%20to%20Rajasthan%20Royals.%20In%20a%20video%2C%20which%20went%20viral%2C%20SRK%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20it's%20a%20very%20proud%20day.%20The%20way%20we%20played%3B%20all%20of%20us.%20I%20won't%20take%20individual%20names%3B%20that's%20been%20done.%20Don't%20feel%20down%2C%20GG.%20We%20will%20all%20bounce%20back.%20It's%20God's%20plan%20for%20today%2C%20as%20Rinku%20says.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20what%20we%20would%20like%20them%20to%20do.%20We'll%20be%20back%20with%20more%20and%20better%2C%20God%20willing.%20Thank%20you%2C%20everyone%2C%20and%20may%20God%20bless%20all.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20other%20owners%20follow%20SRK's%20line%3F%20It's%20completely%20up%20to%20them%2C%20ultimately%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20spend%20the%20money%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20cash-rich%20private%20league%20-%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715239020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fptpm0828_b_625x300_09_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Flsg-owner-sanjiv-goenkas-on-camera-outburst-at-kl-rahul-just-emotion-or-reflection-of-broader-toxic-culture-5623450%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20owner%20Sanjiv%20Goenka%20had%20a%20fiery%20conversation%20with%20skipper%20KL%20Rahul%20following%20their%20big%20loss%20against%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20says%20Biden%20threat%20to%20stop%20arms%20'very%20disappointing'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715238795000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109972780%2Cimgsize-1159447.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-says-biden-threat-to-stop-arms-very-disappointing%2Farticleshow%2F109972780.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109972780.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIsrael's%20ambassador%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20expressed%20disappointment%20Thursday%20at%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20threat%20to%20stop%20certain%20arms%20supplies%20to%20Israel%20if%20it%20invades%20the%20crowded%20Gaza%20city%20of%20Rafah.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20go%20into%20Rafah%2C%20I'm%20not%20supplying%20the%20weapons%20that%20have%20been%20used...%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20cities%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20CNN%2C%20in%20his%20starkest%20warning%20to%20Israel%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-says-biden-threat-to-stop-arms-very-disappointing%2Farticleshow%2F109972780.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-says-biden-threat-to-stop-arms-very-disappointing%2Famp_articleshow%2F109972780.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-says-biden-threat-to-stop-arms-very-disappointing%2Famp_articleshow%2F109972780.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%3A%20Low%20Turnout%20Continues%20in%20Phase%203%20-%20How%20States%20Have%20Performed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fa6hbd04k_voting_640x480_07_May_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20surrounding%20turnout%20persists%20this%20polling%20season%2C%20with%20Phase%203%20recording%20a%20polling%20percentage%20of%2064.6%25%2C%20which%20is%201.7%25%20lower%20than%202019.%20In%20Phase%201%20and%202%2C%20the%20decline%20in%20turnout%20ranged%20between%203%25%20and%204%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20clear%20correlation%20between%20turnouts%20and%20electoral%20outcomes%2C%20various%20theories%20are%20circulating.%20Out%20of%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%201951-52%20to%202019%2C%20turnout%20decreased%20six%20times%20and%20increased%2010%20times%20in%2016%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%201957%20to%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%2010%20instances%20where%20turnout%20increased%2C%20the%20incumbent%20lost%20four%20times%20and%20won%20six%20times.%20Conversely%2C%20out%20of%20the%20six%20instances%20where%20turnout%20declined%2C%20the%20incumbent%20lost%20four%20times%20and%20won%20two%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%2010%20states%20and%20two%20Union%20Territories%20that%20went%20to%20polls%2C%20only%20three%20-%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Goa%2C%20and%20Karnataka%20-%20recorded%20an%20increase%20in%20turnout%20compared%20to%202019.%20Assam%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Dadra%20%26amp%3B%20Nagar%20Haveli%2C%20Daman%20%26amp%3B%20Diu%2C%20Goa%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal%20have%20recorded%20higher%20turnouts%20than%20the%20overall%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrends%20In%20Hindi%20Heartland%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindi%20heartland%20states%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(-2.5%20percentage%20points%2C%20or%20p.p.)%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(-0.6%20p.p.)%2C%20and%20Bihar%20(-3.1%20p.p.)%20appear%20to%20be%20dragging%20down%20the%20overall%20turnout.%20Although%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20numbers%20look%20better%20in%20this%20phase%2C%20these%20states%20have%20consistently%20recorded%20lower%20turnout%20in%20all%20phases.%20The%20unexpected%20inclusion%20in%20this%20group%2C%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20states%20to%20lower%20the%20overall%20turnout%2C%20are%20the%20industrialised%20states%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20scorching%20heat%2C%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20among%20both%20ruling%20party%20and%20opposition%20camps%2C%20voter%20fatigue%20and%20urban%20apathy%20are%20some%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20a%20lower%20turnout%2C%20each%20state%20has%20a%20different%20story%20to%20tell.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAssam%20has%20recorded%20brisk%20voting%2C%20though%20there%20is%20a%20decline%20of%203.4%25%2C%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20higher%20base.%20Similarly%2C%20West%20Bengal%20has%20consistently%20recorded%20high%20voting%20of%20over%2075%25%20in%20all%20three%20phases%2C%20and%20the%20decline%20could%20be%20largely%20attributed%20to%20the%20base%20effect%20here%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20continues%20to%20record%20a%20lower%20turnout%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20among%20the%20lowest%20in%20all%20three%20phases.%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20(JD-U)%20candidates%20were%20in%20the%20fray%20in%20three%20of%20the%20five%20seats.%20It%20seems%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20constant%20flip-flops%20have%20caused%20discontent%20among%20a%20section%20of%20his%20core%20voters.%20It%20may%20also%20be%20the%20case%20that%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20voters%20are%20not%20coming%20out%20wholeheartedly%20to%20support%20JDU%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20both%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%20also%20record%20lower%20turnouts%20in%20state%20polls%20and%20migration%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20same.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGujarat's%20Lower%20Numbers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20home%20turf%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%2C%20the%20turnout%20was%20lower%20than%20in%202019%20by%203.1%20p.p.%20Gujarat%20has%20a%20history%20of%20lower%20turnouts%20in%20state%20elections%20of%202017%20and%202022.%20Here%2C%20the%20near-complete%20demolition%20of%20the%20Congress%20party's%20organisational%20structure%20may%20have%20led%20to%20demotivation%20among%20opposition%20supporters%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20lower%20turnout.%20Additionally%2C%20some%20opposition%20voters%20may%20not%20wish%20to%20vote%20against%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Home%20Minister%2C%20both%20local%20heroes%20who%20are%20leading%20the%20nation%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Gujarati%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20decline%20is%20marginal%20and%20can%20be%20ignored.%20However%2C%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20decline%20of%202.5%20p.p.%20is%20intriguing.%20Baramati%2C%20which%20is%20facing%20a%20Pawar%20versus%20Pawar%20battle%2C%20recorded%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20turnouts%20across%20the%2093%20seats%2C%20at%20only%2056.1%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20high%20hopes%20for%20Maharashtra%20as%20they%20believe%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20could%20enjoy%20a%20sympathy%20factor%20after%20the%20alleged%20'Operation%20Lotus'%20against%20their%20parties.%20However%2C%20the%20numbers%20are%20not%20encouraging%2C%20indicating%20a%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20and%20apathy.%20Parties%20changing%20partners%2C%20dishonouring%20mandates%2C%20and%20the%20constant%20flip-flops%20of%20leaders%20may%20have%20kept%20some%20people%20out%20of%20the%20political%20process.%20Also%2C%20there%20is%20confusion%20among%20a%20section%20of%20voters%20regarding%20future%20realignments.%20Will%20Uddhav%20come%20back%20to%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%3F%20Will%20Ajit%20Pawar%20go%20back%20to%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20or%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%3F%20All%20these%20possibilities%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%20in%20a%20state%20that%20has%20seen%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20Keeping%20UP%20Voters%20Away%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20continues%20to%20record%20a%20lower%20turnout%2C%20among%20the%20lowest%20in%20all%20three%20phases.%20A%20perceived%20done%20deal%20might%20be%20keeping%20opposition%20voters%20out%2C%20or%20complacency%20might%20be%20creeping%20in%20among%20BJP%20supporters%2Fcadre.%20Are%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20supporters%20not%20coming%20out%20to%20vote%2C%20as%20Mayawati%20contesting%20alone%20has%20no%20chance%3F%20Is%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)%20not%20working%20on%20the%20ground%3F%20The%20relative%20turnout%20of%20community%20groups%20is%20also%20important%20in%20the%20state.%20Both%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20have%20put%20up%2020-25%25%20candidates%20who%20were%20earlier%20in%20other%20parties.%20Are%20party%20workers%20not%20wholeheartedly%20working%20for%20these%20newbies%3F%20Turnout%20is%20a%20complex%20phenomenon%20to%20decipher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20analysts%20have%20argued%20that%20since%20the%20voter%20base%20has%20increased%20by%20around%208%20crore%2C%20a%20lower%20turnout%20also%20results%20in%20a%20higher%20number%20of%20votes%20cast%20(in%20absolute%20terms).%20They%20also%20cite%20a%20high%20base%20effect%2C%20with%20a%20high%20turnout%20in%202019%20given%20the%20strong%20nationalism%20fervour%20back%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20also%20intriguing%20that%20states%20that%20witnessed%20turnouts%20of%2070-75%25%20in%20assembly%20polls%20in%20December%202023%20are%20recording%20a%20decline%20of%205-10%20p.p.%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715238780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fa6hbd04k_voting_640x480_07_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-polls-low-turnout-continues-in-phase-3-how-states-have-performed-5623409%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Among%20the%2010%20states%20and%20two%20Union%20Territories%20that%20went%20to%20polls%2C%20only%20three%20-%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Goa%2C%20and%20Karnataka%20-%20recorded%20an%20increase%20in%20turnout%20compared%20to%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-polls-low-turnout-continues-in-phase-3-how-states-have-performed-5623409%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'It%20was%20a%20beautiful%20journey'%3A'%20Aashish%20quits%20Anupamaa%20after%20almost%204%20yrs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715238689000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109972717%2Cimgsize-1353326.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2F