d-sacked-youre-universal-leader-says-mayawatis-nephew-akash-anand-sacked-by-her-5623048%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20shells%20Rafah%20as%20Biden%20warns%20against%20major%20ground%20offensive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715237418000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.files.bbci.co.uk%2Fmodules%2Fbbc-morph-news-waf-page-meta%2F5.3.0%2Fbbc_news_logo.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Flive%2Fworld-68981909%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Heavy%20shelling%20is%20reported%20in%20the%20city%2C%20as%20Joe%20Biden%20says%20the%20US%20won't%20supply%20weapons%20and%20artillery%20shells%20for%20a%20major%20offensive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A48%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Flive%2Fworld-68981909%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20BJP's%20Raebareli%20Candidate%20Feels%20The%20Gandhis%20%26quot%3BHate%26quot%3B%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%20Amethi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20Rae%20Bareli%20candidate%20Dinesh%20Pratap%20Singh%20has%20accused%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20of%20harbouring%20%26quot%3Bhatred%26quot%3B%20for%20Rae%20Bareli-Amethi%2C%20and%20asked%20why%20they%20did%20not%20field%20a%20local%20leader%20but%20opted%20for%20%26quot%3BPriyanka%20Gandhi's%20clerk%26quot%3B%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20from%20Amethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20taking%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20a%20high-profile%20electoral%20contest%20in%20Raebareli%2C%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20Gandhi%20scion%20will%20lose%20by%20a%20bigger%20margin%20than%20his%20mother%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20had%20won%20in%20the%202019%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi%20had%20beaten%20Mr%20Singh%20in%202019%20by%20over%201%2C67%2C000%20votes.%20However%2C%20this%20was%20the%20lowest%20margin%20of%20victory%20that%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20has%20had%20in%20the%20five%20elections%2C%20including%20a%20bypoll%2C%20that%20she%20has%20fought%20from%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20great%20trust%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20under%20his%20leadership%2C%20the%20country%20as%20well%20as%20the%20hard-earned%20income%20of%20the%20people%20is%20safe.%20People%20of%20Rae%20Bareli%20also%20trust%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20in%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20will%20be%20able%20to%20hold%20his%20ground%20before%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20in%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20camping%20in%20Rae%20Bareli%20and%20campaigning%20for%20her%20brother%20Rahul%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20it%20could%20be%20a%20topic%20of%20discussion%20for%20media%20people%20who%20have%20come%20from%20outside%20but%20her%20camping%20here%20was%20a%20non-issue%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Rae%20Bareli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202022%20assembly%20polls%2C%20she%20stayed%20here%20and%20asked%20for%20votes%20in%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%2C%20but%20in%20all%20the%20assembly%20seats%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20camped%20here%20and%20ran%20around%2C%20about%2016%2C000%20votes%20were%20bagged%20in%20assembly%20segments.%20Is%20it%20the%20same%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Congress%20general%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20of%20importance%20to%20you%20but%20she%20holds%20no%20importance%20for%20people%20of%20Rae%20Bareli.%20She%20can%20stay%20here%2C%20it%20will%20be%20very%20good.%20She%20made%20so%20many%20promises%20in%20the%202019%20polls%20and%20till%202024%2C%20leave%20alone%20fulfilling%20those%20promises%2C%20she%20did%20not%20even%20stand%20with%20the%20people%20in%20their%20happy%20and%20sad%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20local%20dialect%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B'Aaj%20nikli%20hain%2C%20humka%20andaza%20hai%20kauno%20gaon%20bachi%20na%20jahan%20belana%20liye%20mahilayein%20khadi%20na%20hui%20hain%2C%20inka%20swagat%20kare%20ke%20liye'%20(I%20have%20an%20idea%20that%20when%20she%20goes%20out%20to%20the%20villages%2C%20women%20would%20welcome%20her%20with%20batons%20in%20their%20hands).%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20alleged%20that%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20has%20hatred%20for%20Rae%20Bareli-Amethi%20and%20that%20is%20why%20it%20neither%20fielded%20anyone%20from%20there%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20since%201952%20nor%20sent%20any%20native%20person%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20ji%20has%20opened%20'mohabbat%20ki%20dukaan'.%20So%20much%20hatred%20is%20filled%20in%20the%20Gandhi%20family's%20mind%20for%20Amethi-Rae%20Bareli.%20From%201952%20till%20now%2C%20Gandhi%20family%20never%20gave%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20ticket%20to%20a%20person%20born%20to%20a%20mother%20from%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20son%20of%20Rae%20Bareli%20was%20sent%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20did%20not%20make%20anyone%20from%20Rae%20Bareli%20even%20an%20MP's%20representative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMP's%20representatives%20have%20also%20been%20brought%20from%20outside.%20Today%20it%20is%20before%20the%20people.%20Could%20only%20a%20person%20brought%20from%20Ludhiana%20who%20is%20Priyanka%20Gandhi's%20clerk%20fight%20the%20polls%20from%20Amethi%3F%20Were%20there%20no%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20Amethi%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20hatred%20that%20they%20have%20for%20Amethi-Rae%20Bareli%2C%20which%20manifests%20itself%20in%20'we%20will%20not%20give%20the%20ticket%20to%20a%20person%20from%20Amethi%20or%20Rae%20Bareli%20but%20get%20a%20person%20from%20Delhi%20or%20Ludhiana'%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20%26quot%3Bhatred%26quot%3B%20for%20Amethi-Rae%20Bareli%20in%20their%20minds%20and%20this%20time%2C%20Amethi-Rae%20Bareli%20will%20give%20a%20befitting%20reply%20to%20them%2C%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20contesting%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20from%20the%20Rae%20Bareli%20seat%2C%20Kishori%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%2C%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20the%20Amethi%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20also%20refuted%20suggestions%20that%20Rae%20Bareli%20was%20an%20electoral%20fortress%20of%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFortress%20is%20one%20which%20has%20four-five%20MLAs%2C%20eight%20block%20pramukhs%2C%2010%20zila%20panchayat%20members%20from%20the%20party.%20The%20Congress%20does%20not%20have%20a%20pradhan%20or%20block%20pramukh%2C%20or%20MLA%2C%20MLC%2C%20or%20zila%20panchayat%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Singh%20claimed%20the%20Congress%20doesn't%20even%20have%20an%20MP%20and%20even%20though%20the%20certificate%20of%20MP%20is%20with%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20but%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20principles%2C%20she%20is%20not%20the%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20fought%20on%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20but%20the%20SP%2C%20BSP%20and%20Apna%20Dal%20(Kamerawadi)%20faction%20supported%20her%20and%20she%20fought%20as%20the%20representative%20of%20four%20parties%2C%20Singh%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20she%20would%20have%20fought%20just%20as%20Congress%20representative%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20my%20vote%2C%20you%20would%20find%20that%20I%20would%20have%20won%20one%20by%20lakhs%20against%20just%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20imagine%20the%20deterioration%20the%20Congress%20has%20suffered%20here.%20In%202019%2C%20when%20I%20fought%20the%20polls%2C%20I%20fought%20on%20the%20scores%20of%202017%20assembly%20polls.%20In%202017%20the%20votes%20of%20all%20assembly%20candidates%20of%20Congress%20was%203%2C40%2C000%20and%20I%20got%203%2C60%2C000%20votes%20and%20now%20when%20the%20Congress%20score%20is%20at%201%2C40%2C000%20votes%20in%202022%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20already%20lost%202%20lakh%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20does%20not%20have%20the%20support%20of%20the%20parties%20that%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20did%2C%20so%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20number%20of%20votes%20by%20which%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20won%20in%202019%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20lose%20by%20a%20bigger%20margin%20than%20that%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20should%20not%20be%20believed%20that%20Congress%20had%20been%20unbeatable%20here%20as%20former%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20defeated%20from%20here%2C%20post%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20say%20so%20do%20not%20know%20the%20history%20of%20Rae%20Bareli.%20In%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20suffered%20a%20crushing%20defeat.%20Those%20who%20say%20Congress%20has%20not%20lost%2C%20they%20should%20be%20told%20that%20Rae%20Bareli%20is%20the%20land%20of%20the%20people%20who%20did%20not%20let%20the%20Britishers%20occupy%20the%20area%20for%20a%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715237340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fp0vm6gh_rahul-gandhi-priyanka-gandhi-rahul-gandhi-ians_625x300_09_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-bjps-raebareli-candidate-dinesh-pratap-singh-feels-the-gandhis-hate-rae-bareli-amethi-5622826%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP's%20Rae%20Bareli%20candidate%20Dinesh%20Pratap%20Singh%20has%20accused%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20of%20harbouring%20%26quot%3Bhatred%26quo