%20dream.%20Their%20most%20significant%20hurdle%20post-launch%20has%20been%20the%20widespread%20lack%20of%20awareness%20surrounding%20millets.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20diligently%20engaged%20in%20consumer%20education%20initiatives%2C%20conducting%20awareness%20campaigns%20in%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20the%20first%20step%20was%20to%20create%20customer%20awareness.%20We%20started%20visiting%20schools%20and%20colleges%20to%20educate%20the%20youth%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20nutritious%20eating%20habits.%20We%20believe%20that%20knowledge%20is%20the%20key%20to%20transformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Shashidhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20take%20students%20on%20a%20factory%20tour%20to%20show%20them%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%20In%202023%2C%20they%20established%20a%20factory%20in%20Trichy%2C%20with%20a%2010%2C000-litre%20capacity%20per%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20opened%20outlets%20in%20Hyderabad%20near%20the%20Statue%20of%20Equality%20and%20one%20in%20Rajahmundry.%20They%20are%20poised%20to%20launch%2010%20to%2012%20more%20outlets%20in%20the%20coming%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20us%2C%20community%20engagement%20is%20equally%20important.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20movement%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20treasures%20of%20our%20ancestors%2C%20adapted%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prabu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20is%20seeing%20an%20increasing%20shift%20towards%20millets%2C%20this%20is%20a%20novel%20way%20to%20include%20them%20in%20our%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Prabu%20Venugopal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715180752000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-ice-cream-1715178095.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F