n%20gnawed%20at%20the%20Surat%20resident%20even%20after%20she%20returned%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20this%20time%20that%20she%20began%20painting%20the%20cover%20pages%20of%20diaries%2C%20which%20were%20highly%20appreciated%20by%20her%20friends%20and%20family.%20Since%20most%20of%20the%20artisans%20she%20visited%20worked%20in%20the%20paper%20industry%2C%20she%20wondered%20if%20she%20could%20turn%20her%20love%20for%20drawing%20and%20painting%20into%20a%20business%20that%20would%20provide%20employment%20to%20people%20who%20worked%20by%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20wanted%20to%20revolutionise%20the%20space%20by%20making%20these%20age-old%20practices%20of%20handmade%20products%20appealing%20to%20today%E2%80%99s%20consumers%20and%20bringing%20them%20back%20into%20trend.%20With%20this%20thought%20in%20mind%2C%20Rashi%20started%20%E2%80%98Roohani%20Rang%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20handmade%20stationery%20business%20that%20sells%20sustainable%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20the%20venture%20stand%20apart%20is%20that%20the%20products%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20diaries%2C%20planners%2C%20calendars%2C%20and%20more%20%E2%80%94%20are%20made%20out%20of%20cotton%20waste.%20So%20far%2C%20Rashi%20has%20sold%20over%2015%2C000%20planners%20and%20employed%20over%2050%20artisans%2C%20while%20recycling%209%2C732%20kg%20of%20cotton.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20trees%20were%20harmed%20in%20making%20this%20paper%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20final%20year%20of%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20at%20the%20Raman%20Bhakta%20School%20of%20Architecture%20in%20Surat%2C%20Rashi%20decided%20to%20venture%20into%20business.%20The%20catch%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%202020%2C%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20COVID-19%20was%20wreaking%20havoc%20across%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20then%20student%20had%20just%20Rs%205%2C000%20to%20start%20her%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%